race.comment: HELL FOLLOWS (8) resumed here in good order over a mile in tougher grade. She has more to give and the step up to 1800m is ideal. Maps for a soft run and Ben Thompson's engagement adds to the confidence. SLUGWORTH (7) was back to his best placing at Gatton over a mile. Won his only start at this distance and should be right in it. VANCITY (10) just missed this track/trip and then came back and was just beaten over 2200m. Drops back to this distance on a 12-day return but given her form she can manage. XTRA LA VITA (3) peaks for the Heathcote yard and has been racing in stronger. The extra metres are likely to suit as should the smaller field size. We are likely to see more from him.
